01:13.840 --> 01:16.999
<i>Once upon a time, I was</i>
<i>the heavyweight champ of New Jersey.</i>

01:17.080 --> 01:19.039
<i>They called me the Bayonne Bleeder.</i>

01:19.120 --> 01:21.849
