01:46.480 --> 01:47.960
without getting shut down,
if you know what I mean.

01:48.040 --> 01:49.599
That's genius right there,
that's what that is.

01:49.680 --> 01:51.353
Hey, no, Champ. You...

01:51.440 --> 01:53.352
- What?
