spruce it up for me a bit.

05:24.840 --> 05:26.399
Come here, give me some sugar.

05:27.240 --> 05:29.311
Come on, Kimby. It's 8:00.

05:29.400 --> 05:30.880
You gotta eat your breakfast. Go. Go, go, go.

05:30.960 --> 05:32.110
Bye, Daddy.

05:41.080 --> 05:42.230
Come here, let me look at you.

05:43.080 --> 05:44.150
I'm all right.

05:44.280 --> 05:45.600
Come here, baby.

05:48.520 --> 05:49.920
