08:39.760 --> 08:42.355
- I got one for all of you.
- How you doin', Champ?

08:42.440 --> 08:44.078
I'm good. How you doin'?

08:45.600 --> 08:47.432
Johnny, how much Wolfschmidts you want?

08:47.520 --> 08:49.398
