you gonna bang me up for two cases?

08:49.480 --> 08:51.517
Well, Johnny, for you,

08:51.600 --> 08:54.513
I'm gonna make you a very special deal.

08:54.600 --> 08:56.398
- Wolfschmidts, right?
- Yeah. Two.

08:57.040 --> 08:59.509
