and you still look good, Champ.

09:10.080 --> 09:11.719
- Hey, Champ.
- How are you?

09:11.800 --> 09:13.120
Hey, Chuck!

09:15.240 --> 09:18.278
Yeah, no, of course. Yeah, but listen...

09:18.360 --> 09:21.319
