isn't that right?

09:21.400 --> 09:23.232
No, no, no.
Hey, calm down a little bit, okay?

09:23.320 --> 09:24.436
What's up?

09:24.520 --> 09:27.160
Listen to me! Listen to me!
All right, listen to me, you fuckin' gonif!

09:29.480 --> 09:31.676
No... I mean...

09:33.240 --> 09:34.833
