10:38.680 --> 10:40.637
Foreman is a fuckin' monster. It's a lock.

10:40.720 --> 10:42.154
I got...

10:43.040 --> 10:44.633
- Title shot, huh?
- That's right, kid.

10:45.360 --> 10:49.320
Hey, this is your lucky day.

10:49.400 --> 10:51.392
AI, lucky day, lucky man.

10:52.400 --> 10:53.754
Come here.

10:53.880 --> 10:55.234
I love you, AI.

10:56.000 --> 10:57.320
Thank you.

10:58.400 --> 11:00.835
- Come on, you're missing it.
- Okay, okay.

11:01.400 --> 11:04.279
<i>Uppercut. Sucker punch.</i>

11:04.360 --> 11:06.397
<i>That night, my favorite movie,</i>

11:06.480 --> 11:08.995
<i>Anthony Quinn,</i> Requiem for a Heavyweight.

11:09.080 --> 11:10.434
<i>Broke my heart, that movie.</i>

11:10.520 --> 11:12.955
<i>You see that, you can't help</i>
<i>but see yourself.</i>

11:13.440 --> 11:15.557
<i>Who have been your past employers?</i>

