Hey, Champ. What the hell? Come with me.

12:42.000 --> 12:45.072
Jimmy! Appreciate it. You know Phyll, right?

12:45.200 --> 12:46.680
- Hey, how you doing?
- Hey, how you doing, Champ?

12:46.760 --> 12:48.672
- I hear you're next on the menu, huh?
- Yeah.

12:48.760 --> 12:50.831
Is that right? You gonna fight Foreman, huh?

12:50.920 --> 12:52.070
That's what they say.

12:52.160 --> 12:53.594
Move it! You got the Champ here!

12:53.680 --> 12:55.319
Hey, how you doin'?

12:55.400 --> 12:56.675
Yo, Bleeder!

12:58.360 --> 13:00.352
- Chuck, just don't...
- It's all right.

13:00.440 --> 13:01.510
Yo.

13:03.720 --> 13:04.790
Hey.

13:06.280 --> 13:07.839
What'd you call me?

13:07.920 --> 13:09.320
The Bleeder, that's what everybody calls you.

13:09.400 --> 13:10.800
The Bayonne Bleeder.

13:11.720 --> 13:14.030
- How you doin'?
- I'm good. You?

13:14.120 --> 13:16.112
- Good. Like the fights, huh?
- Hey.

13:16.200 --> 13:17.395
Sure.

13:17.480 --> 13:19.631
- What the fuck!
- Chuck!

13:21.880 --> 13:24.873
Relax, Champ. Come back for you
when I'm done with Foreman.

13:25.840 --> 13:27.160
Hey, Champ, who you like?

13:27.320 --> 13:29.960
