14:06.000 --> 14:07.593
<i>I'd have said, "Hell no."</i>

14:08.920 --> 14:10.070
<i>But he did it.</i>

14:12.080 --> 14:14.754
<i>What were they gonna do,</i>
<i>put me in the ring with Ali?</i>

14:15.840 --> 14:17.593
Let's go home, baby. Come on.

14:21.680 --> 14:23.911
I don't know,

14:24.000 --> 14:27.357
I think I might hit the diner,
maybe get a cup of coffee or something.

14:27.440 --> 14:29.432
All right. You want company?

14:30.640 --> 14:33.109
No, I gotta walk.

14:33.200 --> 14:34.873
You go home. I'll be all right.

14:37.200 --> 14:38.475
You sure?

14:39.880 --> 14:42.873
Yeah. I just, you know...
I gotta walk, that's all.

14:44.880 --> 14:45.950
Fine.

14:47.320 --> 14:50.279
<i>It was like watching my future</i>
<i>go down the toilet.</i>

14:50.360 --> 14:53.034
<i>Phyll tried to help,</i>
<i>but I was after something else.</i>

14:54.960 --> 14:56.633
<i>Something I shouldn't have.</i>

15:01.800 --> 15:04.235
