32:30.640 --> 32:31.790
<i>He puts on these displays.</i>

32:31.880 --> 32:34.111
<i>Wepner will look slow and awkward,</i>
<i>because he is slow and awkward,</i>

32:34.200 --> 32:36.795
<i>but he does deliver a pretty good blow.</i>

32:36.880 --> 32:39.759
<i>Finally, I get him on the ropes.</i>
<i>He's doing his rope-a-dope thing.</i>

32:39.840 --> 32:41.274
Bayonne, Chuck! Bayonne!

32:41.360 --> 32:42.714
<i>He doesn't give me much.</i>

32:42.800 --> 32:44.120
<i>You know, I take what I can get.</i>

32:44.200 --> 32:48.035
<i>Couple of kidney shots,</i>
<i>behind the head... You know, dirty.</i>

32:51.480 --> 32:53.437
<i>To the best of my knowledge,</i>
<i>that was Muhammad Ali</i>

32:53.520 --> 32:55.352
<i>that was unloading the illegal shots.</i>

32:55.440 --> 32:56.760
Shots to the head.

32:56.840 --> 33:00.038
<i>...if they do penalize him for it or not</i>
<i>is a big question.</i>

33:00.120 --> 33:03.352
<i>But certainly, Muhammad Ali</i>
<i>was no more the winner of that round</i>

33:03.440 --> 33:04.954
<i>than Chuck Wepner.</i>

33:10.960 --> 33:13.475
<i>Ali clearly has a much more fluid motion,</i>

33:13.560 --> 33:14.960
<i>much more ability.</i>

33:15.040 --> 33:16.997
<i>It's clear that he's getting through</i>
<i>with the jab...</i>

33:17.080 --> 33:18.594
Bring your guard up.

33:19.400 --> 33:20.675
<i>There's a quick combination.</i>

33:20.760 --> 33:22.991
<i>Another three, four punches</i>
<i>to the face of Wepner.</i>

33:23.080 --> 33:25.515
<i>But Wepner not visibly shaken,</i>
<i>as he continues to come in.</i>

33:25.600 --> 33:27.034
<i>This man does not back up.</i>

33:27.120 --> 33:29.396
<i>What good was backing up gonna do?</i>

33:29.480 --> 33:30.880
<i>Look, my thing was this.</i>

33:30.960 --> 33:33.520
<i>I couldn't hit him, so I figured</i>
<i>I'd wear him down with my face.</i>

33:33.600 --> 33:37.071
<i>It was working great for five</i>
<i>or six rounds until finally, boom.</i>

33:38.120 --> 33:41.079
<i>Now it looks like Wepner</i>
<i>may possibly have a cut above the eye.</i>

33:41.800 --> 33:43.996
<i>I think I see some red stuff</i>
<i>that might possibly be hair.</i>

33:44.240 --> 33:46.072
<i>No, Wepner is cut above the eye.</i>

33:46.160 --> 33:47.560
<i>Looks like a pretty good gash, too.</i>

33:47.640 --> 33:48.676
Come on!

33:48.760 --> 33:50.035
<i>Wepner holds his arm up and says,</i>

33:50.120 --> 33:51.839
<i>"Come on, Champ,</i>
<i>is that the best you can do?"</i>

33:51.920 --> 33:53.639
<i>Wepner's a tough kid.</i>
<i>There's no doubt about it.</i>

33:53.760 --> 33:56.116
<i>I have tremendous respect</i>
<i>for the courage of this man.</i>

33:56.200 --> 33:58.635
<i>Ali has no respect for his ability.</i>

34:00.040 --> 34:03.556
<i>All I know is they all said</i>
<i>I was gonna be done in three rounds,</i>

34:03.640 --> 34:05.233
<i>and now they're chanting my name.</i>

34:05.320 --> 34:09.199
<i>Sure, he was beating the crap out</i>
<i>of me, but they loved it. They loved me.</i>

34:09.280 --> 34:10.429
Hey, John!

34:10.520 --> 34:14.434
You hear that crowd, Chuck?
They love you, Chuck! They love you!

34:16.480 --> 34:18.039
- Hey!
- What?

34:18.159 --> 34:20.550
Look at me, you dumb fuck. Focus!

34:22.080 --> 34:25.391
<i>Wepner not concerned with the left jab</i>
<i>at all, he just takes the punch.</i>

34:25.480 --> 34:29.474
<i>Ali fakes the top part of his body back</i>
<i>and slips a punch to his left and...</i>

34:32.080 --> 34:36.074
<i>Vicious shot to the ribs</i>
<i>of Muhammad Ali, and what a surprise!</i>

34:36.159 --> 34:39.312
<i>Chuck Wepner gets to the body</i>
<i>of Muhammad Ali!</i>

34:40.280 --> 34:41.953
Chuck! Holy shit!

34:42.040 --> 34:45.875
<i>I was as shocked as anyone else.</i>
<i>I mean, my head was spinning.</i>

34:46.840 --> 34:49.560
<i>I knew I hit him hard,</i>
<i>but to see him on his ass like that...</i>

34:50.320 --> 34:53.916
<i>I saw myself as</i>
<i>the heavyweight champion of the world.</i>

34:54.000 --> 34:57.596
<i>Didn't last, though. He got back up.</i>
<i>Boy, was he pissed.</i>

34:57.680 --> 35:01.435
<i>Ali is now going to have to</i>
<i>get off his haunches and start the fight!</i>

35:01.520 --> 35:04.194
<i>This is no joke! Ali was surprised!</i>

35:05.560 --> 35:07.836
<i>Ali sat right down on his seat.</i>

35:07.920 --> 35:10.116
<i>Now watch Ali go to work.</i>

35:10.200 --> 35:13.671
<i>Ali is aggravated.</i>
<i>It looks like Wepner's in trouble now.</i>

35:23.520 --> 35:26.957
<i>By the 12th round, he'd already closed</i>
<i>both my eyes, broke my nose,</i>

35:27.040 --> 35:29.839
<i>and he was still dancing circles around me.</i>

35:29.920 --> 35:31.752
<i>I didn't care.</i>

35:31.840 --> 35:33.877
<i>I was just happy to be in the ring with him.</i>

35:35.400 --> 35:38.950
<i>I don't remember much after that,</i>
<i>except trying to stay on my feet.</i>

35:39.680 --> 35:43.799
<i>I could feel him hitting me.</i>
<i>No pain, just the thud of his fists.</i>

35:43.880 --> 35:44.870
<i>Bone on bone.</i>

35:45.480 --> 35:46.470
<i>Boom.</i>

35:47.480 --> 35:48.470
<i>Boom.</i>

35:49.360 --> 35:52.034
<i>Stay up, Chuck. Stay up.</i>

35:53.400 --> 35:57.314
<i>Round 15, the heavyweight</i>
<i>championship of the world!</i>

35:57.400 --> 35:59.596
<i>People are on their feet at the Coliseum.</i>

35:59.680 --> 36:01.000
<i>They are seeing a better fight</i>

36:01.080 --> 36:03.549
<i>than they thought that they were</i>
<i>going to see for their money.</i>

36:03.680 --> 36:06.115
<i>Mohammed Ali wants to knock this man out.</i>

36:06.200 --> 36:08.317
<i>Wepner does not want to go down.</i>

36:08.400 --> 36:11.040
<i>There's a good combination,</i>
<i>Wepner's ready to go.</i>

36:11.120 --> 36:15.637
<i>Ali comes on. Wepner is staggering,</i>
<i>he's out on his feet right now.</i>

36:15.720 --> 36:18.030
<i>Ali has his man in trouble!</i>

36:18.120 --> 36:20.589
<i>Wepner attempting to hang on viciously.</i>

36:20.680 --> 36:23.275
<i>He's trying to hang on. He's out on his feet!</i>

36:23.360 --> 36:24.919
<i>Ali clocks him!</i>

36:26.320 --> 36:30.280
<i>A right hand and a left hook</i>
<i>drops Chuck Wepner!</i>

36:32.080 --> 36:33.150
Get up! Get up!

36:33.240 --> 36:37.075
<i>Five. Six. Seven. Eight.</i>

36:37.160 --> 36:38.640
<i>The referee stops the fight!</i>

36:38.720 --> 36:41.713
<i>It'll be scored as a technical knockout!</i>

36:41.800 --> 36:46.113
<i>Muhammad Ali retains the heavyweight</i>
<i>championship of the world!</i>

38:12.280 --> 38:14.158
<i>Nineteen seconds.</i>

38:14.240 --> 38:16.755
<i>They stopped the fight with 19 seconds to go.</i>

38:16.880 --> 38:18.234
<i>I didn't make it.</i>

38:19.400 --> 38:23.440
<i>Funny thing is, nobody cared.</i>
<i>They threw me a party anyway.</i>

38:27.920 --> 38:30.230
AI says to me,
"Forget the bank, we need a fire hose

38:30.320 --> 38:32.118
"'cause Ali's getting up
and his ass is burnin'!"

38:34.760 --> 38:38.276
<i>And what a reception for you in Bayonne.</i>

38:38.360 --> 38:40.079
<i>Yeah, that was some party, huh?</i>

38:40.800 --> 38:44.316
<i>You think there'll be a rematch, Chuck?</i>
<i>You and Ali, one more time?</i>

38:44.400 --> 38:46.517
<i>Could be. Why not?</i>

38:46.600 --> 38:48.910
<i>You know, unless he's too scared of me now.</i>

38:49.520 --> 38:52.240
<i>In the meantime, Bob,</i>
<i>I'm just gonna enjoy myself.</i>

38:52.320 --> 38:53.640
Chuck, you look good.

38:53.720 --> 38:55.200
<i>And what do you do for enjoyment, Chuck?</i>

38:55.280 --> 38:56.999
<i>Wine, women, and song, Bob.</i>

38:57.080 --> 38:59.959
<i>Wine, women, and song.</i>
<i>Not necessarily in that order.</i>

39:00.040 --> 39:01.235
<i>Okay.</i>

39:01.320 --> 39:02.720
<i>Guess what I like first.</i>

39:02.800 --> 39:04.359
<i>I'll leave that for the folks at home.</i>

39:04.440 --> 39:06.352
<i>Getting back to the fight.</i>

39:06.440 --> 39:09.672
<i>This photograph</i>
<i>is of the knockdown in round nine.</i>

39:09.760 --> 39:10.750
Come on.

39:10.840 --> 39:14.231
<i>Now, Ali says that's your foot</i>
<i>stepping on his foot.</i>

39:14.320 --> 39:17.518
<i>And he said it threw him off-balance,</i>
<i>and that's why he went down.</i>

39:17.600 --> 39:18.829
Bullshit. Not even close.

39:18.960 --> 39:21.031
I step on your foot, you goin' down,
you protest, wouldn't you?

39:21.120 --> 39:23.635
Of course, that'd be the first thing
you do. You stand up and you say...

39:23.720 --> 39:26.030
Referee calls it a knockdown
and it's in the books. It's a knockdown.

39:26.120 --> 39:27.076
That's why there's a referee there.

39:27.160 --> 39:28.719
- Daddy.
- Yeah, honey.

39:28.800 --> 39:30.359
This guy's just trying to
make something, you know?

39:30.440 --> 39:31.590
Daddy.

39:32.520 --> 39:34.637
<i>- Ali knows what happened.</i>
- Oh, my God.

39:34.720 --> 39:36.393
- Is that supposed to be me?
- Yeah.

39:36.480 --> 39:37.994
Look at this.

39:38.080 --> 39:39.309
Who is that, Bigfoot?

39:39.400 --> 39:40.800
No, it's Daddy.

39:40.880 --> 39:42.473
That's my girl.

39:48.760 --> 39:50.353
I'll be right back.

39:52.200 --> 39:54.396
- What are you doing?
- Just leave me alone.

39:54.480 --> 39:56.392
Don't you wanna watch the show? It's still...

39:57.320 --> 40:00.199
- You kidding me, Chuck?
- What?

40:00.280 --> 40:03.910
What, "Wine, women, and song"? On television?

40:04.000 --> 40:08.199
You know, it's bad enough
what you do on the streets, but on TV!

40:08.280 --> 40:12.035
I said "woman," not women.
I said one woman. You.

40:12.120 --> 40:13.873
- Bullshit.
- Come on, Phyll.

40:14.120 --> 40:15.839
I'm just mouthing off.
You know what it's like.

40:16.040 --> 40:18.760
No, I don't know what it's like, Chuck.
And I don't care.

40:18.840 --> 40:21.400
It was a big night for me, all right?

40:21.520 --> 40:23.876
We're just having fun.
They were all, you know...

40:27.200 --> 40:31.160
They were eating it up, you know?
I was doing the Bayonne thing.

40:31.280 --> 40:32.430
They loved it.

40:32.760 --> 40:36.549
Yeah. Everybody loves you.

40:41.600 --> 40:44.115
<i>I didn't hear a freakin' word she said.</i>

40:44.200 --> 40:46.590
<i>Truth is, I was so high on cloud nine,</i>

40:46.680 --> 40:49.275
<i>I couldn't hear anything</i>
<i>but the sound of my own voice.</i>

40:49.360 --> 40:51.272
And I buy her this beautiful
powder blue negligee.

40:51.360 --> 40:54.110
And I says, "Honey, I want you to
wear this tonight, because tonight,

40:54.200 --> 40:57.159
"you're gonna be sleeping with
the heavyweight champion of the world."

40:57.240 --> 40:59.880
So, after the fight,
I come back to the hotel, I let myself in,

40:59.960 --> 41:03.032
she says to me, "So, do I go to
Ali's room, or does he come to mine?"

41:08.840 --> 41:10.479
How you doin' for Smirnoff?

41:10.560 --> 41:12.279
Good, Champ. I'll take whatever you got.

41:12.360 --> 41:13.635
People doing a lot of celebrating this week.

41:13.720 --> 41:14.836
That's what I like to hear.

41:14.920 --> 41:17.560
Hey, Red, do me a favor.
Give me a round for everybody on me.

41:17.640 --> 41:19.632
Wait your turn. I got customers.

41:19.720 --> 41:22.155
- Wait my turn?
- Easy, Chuck. Chuck, easy, easy, easy.

41:22.240 --> 41:24.357
That's Linda. You don't wanna mess with her.

41:24.440 --> 41:26.318
Linda! Linda, come here.

41:26.400 --> 41:27.800
Don't you know who this is?

41:27.920 --> 41:29.479
Yeah, the Bayonne Bleeder.

41:29.560 --> 41:30.676
How you doin'?

41:30.800 --> 41:33.315
Ali says you stepped on his foot,
that's why he went down.

41:33.400 --> 41:35.995
Yeah? He said that? Well, that's bullshit.

41:36.080 --> 41:39.118
That's what he said.
Dirty fighter. Called you a punk.

41:41.240 --> 41:43.960
Punk, huh? I ain't no punk.

41:44.040 --> 41:47.078
I was almost the heavyweight champion
of the world.

41:47.160 --> 41:49.516
Well, you're no Mountain Rivera.

41:49.600 --> 41:51.353
Wait a minute, you saw that movie?

41:51.440 --> 41:53.318
<i>Requiem for a Heavyweight?</i> Sure.

41:53.400 --> 41:54.516
Fuck me.

41:54.600 --> 41:56.319
Not in this lifetime.

41:56.720 --> 41:59.918
But now it's your turn.
So, what are you having?

42:02.760 --> 42:05.559
I'll have a vodka rocks, and
whatever these jim-jims are drinking.

42:05.640 --> 42:06.710
Sure.

42:06.800 --> 42:08.519
- Thanks, Champ.
- What'd you say her name was?

42:08.600 --> 42:09.795
Linda. Linda.

42:16.360 --> 42:17.999
Here you go. Sorry for the wait.

42:20.720 --> 42:22.712
Hey, Chuck. Show her that ring.

42:22.800 --> 42:24.439
- What?
- Show her that ring.

42:26.120 --> 42:29.557
I designed it. It's a metaphor.

42:29.640 --> 42:32.360
The black onyx represents Ali.
I'm the diamond.

42:32.440 --> 42:35.877
Yeah? If I was you, I'd find
the gumball machine you got it from

42:35.960 --> 42:37.110
and get my quarter back.

42:39.480 --> 42:40.880
Let me ask you something. What sign are you?

42:40.960 --> 42:43.236
- You're kidding, right?
- Dead serious.

42:43.320 --> 42:44.549
Pisces.

42:44.640 --> 42:47.394
- No shit! That's my sign!
- Like that's not a line.

42:47.480 --> 42:49.278
- I'm not lying to you.
- What's your birthday, big shot?

42:49.360 --> 42:51.955
February 26th. What?

42:52.720 --> 42:54.598
- That's my birthday.
- Shut up.

42:54.680 --> 42:56.911
- No, that's my birthday!
- Come on.

42:57.000 --> 42:58.150
Here, look at this.

43:02.600 --> 43:04.080
Linda Pandilano.

43:06.080 --> 43:08.231
Anybody ever tell you
you take a beautiful picture?

43:08.320 --> 43:09.800
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

43:09.880 --> 43:13.556
No, I'm serious.
Hey, I'm so in love right now, it hurts.

43:13.640 --> 43:15.154
What are you doing later on?
Let's get married.

43:15.360 --> 43:17.511
Sure. Let me call your wife.

43:21.200 --> 43:23.840
Look, Chuck, you don't know nothing about me.

43:23.920 --> 43:26.594
And I don't know nothing about you.
So, what are you doing?

43:49.040 --> 43:50.190
Put this one over here.

43:54.040 --> 43:56.714
That's pretty.
Chuck. Will you get it? I'm busy.

43:58.840 --> 44:01.309
Yeah. This one's so cute.

44:02.240 --> 44:04.709
Hello? Yeah, this is him.

44:05.760 --> 44:06.830
What?

44:07.400 --> 44:10.472
<i>About a year and a half after the fight,</i>
<i>I get a phone call.</i>

44:10.560 --> 44:12.677
<i>Guy says he's a producer in Hollywood.</i>

44:12.760 --> 44:17.118
<i>Says some guy named Stallone wrote a</i>
<i>screenplay inspired by me. I was like...</i>

44:17.240 --> 44:18.356
What?

44:38.880 --> 44:40.792
<i>That don't matter either, you know?</i>

44:42.040 --> 44:44.509
<i>So, I was thinkin'...</i>

44:44.600 --> 44:47.195
<i>It really don't matter if I lose this fight.</i>

44:48.360 --> 44:51.114
<i>It really don't matter</i>
<i>if this guy opens my head, either.</i>

44:53.520 --> 44:55.591
<i>'Cause all I wanna do is go the distance.</i>

44:57.440 --> 44:59.909
- Chuck?
- I know.

45:00.000 --> 45:03.038
<i>Nobody's ever gone the distance with Creed.</i>

45:03.120 --> 45:04.918
<i>And if I can go that distance,</i>

45:06.880 --> 45:09.793
<i>just hearing that bell ring,</i>
<i>you know, I'm still standing...</i>

45:17.200 --> 45:20.398
Chuck Wepner. You're Chuck Wepner, right?

45:20.480 --> 45:21.755
- Hey, how you doin'?
- It's nice to meet you.

45:21.840 --> 45:24.435
- Nice to meet you.
- It's Chuck Wepner, guys.

45:24.520 --> 45:25.840
The real Rocky!

45:27.320 --> 45:28.720
<i>You hear that?</i>

45:28.800 --> 45:31.315
<i>Chuck Wepner, the real Rocky.</i>

45:33.000 --> 45:34.559
<i>I told you you know me.</i>

45:34.640 --> 45:38.236
Thank you very much.
Bye, everybody. Come on. Let's go.

45:39.480 --> 45:43.076
<i>I felt like a movie star.</i>
<i>This guy, he really got me.</i>

45:43.160 --> 45:45.959
<i>The job as a debt collector,</i>
<i>running the steps,</i>

45:46.040 --> 45:48.760
<i>even the conversation I had</i>
<i>with my wife, for Christ sakes.</i>

45:48.840 --> 45:51.878
<i>That was me. I was Rocky.</i>

46:13.440 --> 46:16.512
<i>Ladies and gents,</i>
<i>look who just walked in here!</i>

46:16.680 --> 46:18.637
<i>It's the king himself!</i>

46:18.720 --> 46:21.599
<i>It's the guy who went 15 rounds</i>
<i>with Muhammad Ali!</i>

46:21.680 --> 46:24.400
<i>The real life Rocky Balboa!</i>

46:24.480 --> 46:27.951
<i>Come on, and the toughest</i>
<i>son of a bitch in the Garden State!</i>

46:28.040 --> 46:31.078
<i>Give it up for Chuck Wepner!</i>

46:35.360 --> 46:36.476
Thank you!

46:36.560 --> 46:39.280
Hey, there he is! Yeah!

46:39.400 --> 46:41.551
All right! All right!

46:55.600 --> 46:57.319
<i>How about that band?</i>

46:57.400 --> 46:58.914
<i>Hit movie, hit song.</i>

46:59.000 --> 47:00.320
<i>What can I say?</i>

47:00.400 --> 47:02.039
<i>I'm a lucky guy.</i>

47:26.600 --> 47:27.590
Having fun tonight?

47:29.240 --> 47:31.232
Go get a drink. How you doing?

47:33.120 --> 47:35.112
This will be right here.

47:36.040 --> 47:37.997
Hey, John, look at that.

47:39.280 --> 47:40.350
Yo, Champ!

47:40.440 --> 47:43.956
I gotta tell you,
that movie was fuckin' unbelievable.

47:44.040 --> 47:45.076
Thanks, pal. Appreciate it.

47:45.160 --> 47:47.356
- How many nominations you get?
- Ten.

47:47.440 --> 47:49.636
Best Picture, Best Actor, Best Director...

47:49.760 --> 47:52.798
Holy shit! You must've made
a fuckin' fortune! Am I right?

47:52.880 --> 47:54.997
- I'm gonna let you in on a little secret.
- Yeah.

47:55.080 --> 47:56.992
When Sly told me about <i>Rocky,</i>

47:57.080 --> 48:00.232
he offered me 70 G's or 1% of the box office.

48:00.320 --> 48:01.356
I took the 70 G's.

48:01.480 --> 48:03.312
What do I know about movies?
I'm from Bayonne, you know?

48:03.440 --> 48:04.874
Hey, a bird in the hand, am I right?

48:04.960 --> 48:08.397
Hey, bird in the hand is good as
a hand in the bush <i>. Capisce?</i>

48:08.480 --> 48:09.994
Double <i>capisce!</i>

48:11.360 --> 48:14.558
Hey, doll, set my man up
with whatever he wants! On me!

48:14.640 --> 48:16.313
- Right on. Thanks, Champ.
- All right.

48:16.400 --> 48:17.390
All right, pal.

48:17.480 --> 48:19.517
You got 70 grand for that?

48:20.120 --> 48:21.190
Shut up, John.

48:21.280 --> 48:23.237
You hear that? 70 G's.

48:23.320 --> 48:24.276
What?

48:24.360 --> 48:26.113
Chuck got 70 big ones for <i>Rocky!</i>

48:26.200 --> 48:28.078
John, John, would you
shut the fuck up, please?

48:28.160 --> 48:29.560
